commit c1aea05a4ab27c93d8664a6d1803a4a5cb936bb3
Author: Oliver Kurth <okurth@vmware.com>
Date:   Wed Nov 15 13:32:55 2017 -0800

    DragNDrop plugin change for VMware Tools on Windows; not applicable to
