          ->setBufferSize (SO_{SND|RCV}BUF), ->setSendLowLatencyMode() (non-native
          option regarding buffering/callback behavior).
    
      lib/rpcIn/rpcin.c:
      services/plugins/grabbitmqProxy/grabbitmqProxyPlugin.c:
